rows.label: bf09300100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ][ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf09300100_0020
rows.name: Blades eventually transform into Divine Beasts...

rows.label: bf09300100_0030
rows.name: And they give birth to many new Blades.

rows.label: bf09300100_0040
rows.name:
They even become part of the world itself...
And the cycle continues, doesn't it?

rows.label: bf09300100_0050
rows.name: It's amazing.

rows.label: bf09300100_0052
rows.name: I'm truly envious.

rows.label: bf09300100_0060
rows.name: Envious...of us?

rows.label: bf09300100_0070
rows.name: I'd like to ask God something.

rows.label: bf09300100_0080
rows.name: About Homura, Hikari, and all of you...

rows.label: bf09300100_0090
rows.name: Why did he create such incredible beings?

rows.label: bf09300100_0100
rows.name: Actually, I think I already have an idea.

rows.label: bf09300100_0110
rows.name: So I want to check the answer.

rows.label: bf09300100_0120
rows.name: Check the answer...?

rows.label: bf09300100_0130
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: bf09300100_0140
rows.name: You claim to know the reason for our existence?

rows.label: bf09300100_0150
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hrk-!

rows.label: bf09300100_0160
rows.name: Shin!

rows.label: bf09300100_0170
rows.name: Yoshitsune! Benkei!

rows.label: bf09300100_0180
rows.name: Benkei...

rows.label: bf09300100_0190
rows.name: I won't let you harm Shin.

rows.label: bf09300100_0200
rows.name: Stand down, Benkei.

rows.label: bf09300100_0210
rows.name: But-!

rows.label: bf09300100_0220
rows.name:
Our part ends here.
Nothing has been in vain.

rows.label: bf09300100_0230
rows.name: We've done what we set out to do.

rows.label: bf09300100_0240
rows.name: Shin...

rows.label: bf09300100_0250
rows.name: Nia...

rows.label: bf09300100_0260
rows.name: W-what?

rows.label: bf09300100_0270
rows.name: C-can you use your power to help Shin...?

rows.label: bf09300100_0280
rows.name:
Y-yes...
If first aid is enough...

rows.label: bf09300100_0290
rows.name: I won't thank you, you know.

rows.label: bf09300100_0300
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ][ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf09300100_0310
rows.name:
I'll go ahead and
prepare for Shin's treatment.

rows.label: bf09300100_0320
rows.name: Yoshitsune, take care of Shin, will you?

rows.label: bf09300100_0330
rows.name: Yeah, got iâ€”

rows.label: bf09300100_0332
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]DISTRESS

rows.label: bf09300100_0335
rows.name: Benkei!!!

rows.label: bf09300100_0340
rows.name: I won't let you climb any further...

rows.label: bf09300100_0350
rows.name: M-Marveni?! Here?!

rows.label: bf09300100_0360
rows.name: But why does he look like that?!

rows.label: bf09300100_0370
rows.name:
If God sent Blades to this world,
it was for my benefit.

rows.label: bf09300100_0380
rows.name:
To find cores containing more powerful,
more innovative, and uniquely rare data.

rows.label: bf09300100_0390
rows.name: For that selection, I began the baptism.

rows.label: bf09300100_0400
rows.name: And here you see the result.

rows.label: bf09300100_0410
rows.name: You bastard...

rows.label: bf09300100_0420
rows.name: So he took the cores from all those Blades...

rows.label: bf09300100_0430
rows.name: So that's what the baptism was for...

rows.label: bf09300100_0440
rows.name: I am the executor of God's will.

rows.label: bf09300100_0450
rows.name: What are you saying?

rows.label: bf09300100_0460
rows.name: Such arrogance...

rows.label: bf09300100_0470
rows.name: Who are you to make such decisions?!

rows.label: bf09300100_0480
rows.name: Keep your delusions to yourself.

rows.label: bf09300100_0490
rows.name:
It's not a delusion.
Have you forgotten the power of Heaven's Holy Grail?

rows.label: bf09300100_0500
rows.name: That power...

rows.label: bf09300100_0510
rows.name:
The power to erase existences unworthy of life,
doesn't the Holy Grail have that?

rows.label: bf09300100_0520
rows.name: Isn't that the will of God?

rows.label: bf09300100_0530
rows.name: Homura and Hikari aren't like that!

rows.label: bf09300100_0540
rows.name: ...I understand now...

rows.label: bf09300100_0550
rows.name:
Why Metsu is so fixated
on the world's destruction.

rows.label: bf09300100_0560
rows.name: It's you, Marveni.

rows.label: bf09300100_0570
rows.name: Metsu has been corrupted by your influence...

rows.label: bf09300100_0580
rows.name:
So what if that's the case?
What's the problem?

rows.label: bf09300100_0590
rows.name: Haven't you traveled throughout Alst?

rows.label: bf09300100_0600
rows.name: Surely you've witnessed the state of Mors?

rows.label: bf09300100_0610
rows.name:
Even after countless ages, 
humans haven't changed at all.
